data.description: Gorgeous home in Gardnerville Ranchos w/ covered front & rear patios where you can enjoy the views of the mountains. Large living area with beautiful flooring throughout. This home has 3 bedrooms 2 full baths and a kitchen that opens to the dining area for easy entertaining. Kitchen features granite counter-tops, custom cabinetry & flooring, and includes the refrigerator. The laundry room is fully equipped with washer, dryer, & shelving. Storage shed in backyard with low maintenance landscaping! MUST SEE.
